6.1 Authentication Requirements
FR-AUTH-001

The system SHALL support GitHub OAuth authentication.

Acceptance Criteria

Given a valid GitHub account
When a user authenticates via OAuth
Then the user SHALL gain access to the application.

FR-AUTH-002

The system SHALL create user accounts automatically after first successful login.

FR-AUTH-003

The system SHALL maintain authenticated sessions securely.

Constraints
Sessions SHALL expire after 24 hours of inactivity.
Tokens SHALL NOT be stored in plaintext.
FR-AUTH-004

The system SHALL deny access to unauthorized users.

6.2 Project Requirements
FR-PROJ-001

Users SHALL be able to connect GitHub repositories.

Acceptance Criteria

Given a connected GitHub account
When a repository is selected
Then the repository SHALL appear in the dashboard.

FR-PROJ-002

The system SHALL support multiple projects per user.

FR-PROJ-003

Projects SHALL display:

Repository activity
Commit metrics
Pull request metrics
Contributor activity
Risk indicators
AI recommendations
FR-PROJ-004

The dashboard SHALL refresh automatically every 60 seconds.

FR-PROJ-005

The system SHALL maintain historical project metrics.

Retention:

Minimum retention SHALL be 365 days.
6.3 Dashboard Requirements
FR-DASH-001

The dashboard SHALL display:

Project health score
Open pull requests
Commit frequency
Team activity
Repository alerts
Risk indicators
FR-DASH-002

Dashboard load time SHALL remain below 3 seconds under normal operating conditions.

FR-DASH-003

The dashboard SHALL support:

Search
Sorting
Filtering
FR-DASH-004

Users SHALL be able to filter projects by:

Risk level
Activity level
Assigned users
Repository
6.4 AI Recommendation Requirements
FR-AI-001

The system SHALL generate AI-assisted recommendations using statistical analysis.

FR-AI-002

AI recommendations SHALL include:

Risk explanation
Suggested intervention
Confidence level
FR-AI-003

The AI system SHALL analyze:

Commit activity
Pull request velocity
Activity trends
Contributor engagement
FR-AI-004

The system SHALL classify projects into:

Healthy
Warning
At Risk
FR-AI-005

AI processing SHALL complete within 30 seconds after new repository ingestion.

6.5 Notification Requirements
FR-NOTIF-001

The system SHALL generate notifications for:

Risk escalation
Repository inactivity
Pull request stagnation
Deadline proximity
FR-NOTIF-002

Notifications SHALL support:

In-app delivery
Email delivery
FR-NOTIF-003

Users SHALL be able to configure notification preferences.

6.6 Search Requirements
FR-SEARCH-001

Users SHALL be able to search:

Projects
Repositories
Users
Activities
FR-SEARCH-002

Search results SHALL return within 2 seconds for datasets under 100,000 records.

6.7 Analytics Requirements
FR-ANALYTICS-001

The system SHALL track:

Daily active users
Repository activity
Feature usage
Notification interactions
FR-ANALYTICS-002

Analytics SHALL support historical trend visualization.

6.8 Access Control Requirements
FR-RBAC-001

The system SHALL implement role-based access control.

FR-RBAC-002

Unauthorized resource access SHALL return HTTP 403 responses.

FR-RBAC-003

Permission changes SHALL be audit logged.